#: ../content/pages/faq.md:block 60 (paragraph)
msgid ""
"First, see the explanation of [Web Workers](#what-are-web-workers-and-what-"
"are-the-threats-that-i-face)."
msgstr ""
"Во-первых, посмотрите объяснение [Web Workers](#what-are-web-workers-and-"
"what-are-the-threats-that-i-face)."

#: ../content/pages/faq.md:block 61 (paragraph)
msgid ""
"See the [answer to the video question](#how-can-i-fix-videos-if-they-fail-to-"
"play-or-retrieve-data-in-time)."
msgstr ""
"Смотрите [ответ на вопрос о видео](#how-can-i-fix-videos-if-they-fail-to-"
"play-or-retrieve-data-in-time)."

#: ../content/pages/faq.md:block 62 (paragraph)
msgid ""
"If you find a website that needs WebWorker protection set to `Strict` and "
