"[issue tracker](https://pagure.io/JShelter/webextension/issues) или "
"отправьте нам [e-mail](mailto:jshelter@gnu.org)."

#: ../content/pages/faq.md:block 63 (header)
msgid "User interface issues"
msgstr "Проблемы с пользовательским интерфейсом"

#: ../content/pages/faq.md:block 64 (header)
msgid ""
"Can I see a JShelter (badge) icon next to my navigation bar? I want to "
