#: ../content/pages/home-tmp.md:block 17 (header)
msgid "Contribute"
msgstr "Вклад"

#: ../content/pages/home-tmp.md:block 18 (header)
msgid "I found a bug!"
msgstr "Я нашел ошибку!"

#: ../content/pages/home-tmp.md:block 19 (paragraph)
msgid ""
"If you have any questions or you spotted a bug, the project's [issue tracker]"
"(https://pagure.io/JShelter/webextension/issues \"https://pagure.io/JShelter/"
"webextension/issues\") is the place for posting those. We especially "
"appreciate feedback, so feel free to use the issue tracker for chiming in."
msgstr ""
"Если у вас есть вопросы или вы заметили ошибку, вы можете написать об этом в "
"[issue tracker](https://pagure.io/JShelter/webextension/issues "
"\"https://pagure.io/JShelter/webextension/issues\"). Мы особенно ценим "
"обратную связь, поэтому не стесняйтесь использовать issue tracker для "
"сообщений."

#: ../content/pages/home-tmp.md:block 20 (header)
msgid "How can I help?"
msgstr "Как я могу помочь?"

#: ../content/pages/home-tmp.md:block 21 (paragraph)
msgid ""
"Using JShelter and reporting any problems you find in our [issue tracker]"
"(https://pagure.io/JShelter/webextension/issues \"https://pagure.io/JShelter/"
"webextension/issues\") is a huge help. If you want to contribute to the "
"project itself, post your ideas on the issue tracker or just go ahead and "
"make a pull request."
msgstr ""
"Использование JShelter и сообщения о найденных проблемах в нашем "
"[issue tracker](https://pagure.io/JShelter/webextension/issues "
"\"https://pagure.io/JShelter/webextension/issues\") - это огромная помощь. "
"Если вы хотите внести свой вклад в сам проект, опубликуйте свои идеи на "
"трекере проблем или просто сделайте pull request."

#: ../content/pages/home-tmp.md:block 22 (header)
msgid "What is the license?"
msgstr "Что такое лицензия?"

#: ../content/pages/home-tmp.md:block 23 (paragraph)
msgid ""
"JShelter is copylefted software, available under the [GNU General Public "
"License](/license/ \"/license/\")."
msgstr ""
"JShelter - это программное обеспечение с авторским левом, доступное на "
"условиях [GNU General Public License] (/license/ \"/license/\")."
